---
import Photo from '../components/Photo.astro';
import death from '../assets/death.jpeg';
---

<section
	id='expectations'
	class='container py-5 d-flex flex-column align-items-stretch row-gap-4 row-gap-lg-5'
>
	<div class='row justify-content-center align-items-center row-gap-3'>
		<div class='col-5 col-md-4'>
			<Photo
				photo={death}
				alt='Olivia after eating blueberries for the first time'
			/>
		</div>
		<div class='col-12 col-md-6 text-center text-md-start'>
			<h2 class='display-2 mb-0'>What to expect</h2>
			<p class='fs-6'>
				Join us for a day filled with joy, laughter, and a touch of
				Korean tradition. Here's what you can look forward to:
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div
		class='row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-auto row-cols-lg-3 row-gap-4 text-center'
	>
		<div class='col'>
			<h3 class='display-3'>🕰️ Times are loose</h3>
			<p class='fs-6'>
				The party will generally be 3 – 5pm, but don't feel obligated to
				stick around till the end or to show up <em>exactly</em> on time.
				We're just excited to see you!
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class='col'>
			<h3 class='display-3'>🥢 Korean-American Cuisine</h3>
			<p class='fs-6'>
				We'll have light (egg-and-peanut-free) snacks from both sides of
				the world: charcuterie boards and Korean staples like <a
					href='https://www.maangchi.com/recipe/japchae'
					target='_blank'
					>japchae</a
				>
				and <a
					href='https://www.maangchi.com/recipe/gimbap'
					target='_blank'
					>kimbap</a
				>!
			</p>
			<p class='fs-6'>
				There will be waters and sodas, and we'll even have a fun soju
				cocktail 🍹
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class='col'>
			<h3 class='display-3'>🎂 Singing & Cake</h3>
			<p class='fs-6'>
				Around 4, we'll gather to sing "Happy Birthday" and watch Olivia
				smash her cake!
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
